title: SWF_Protect_Remover_2.0.1
description:
SWF Protect Remover 2.0.1

                                We all like this word: FREE

I wanted to convert a swf file but i could not cause it had protection in it.So off i went to to the wonderful world web and found this and worked like a charm.

SWF Protect Remover will allow you to delete protection tags with the password or without it (tags for protection against editing) from files of any versions of the SWF Flash format. The program has a built-in player of SWF-files. SWF Protect Remover can work with the packed SWF-files and pack them after processing. The program is simple in utilization, all the actions are carried out by means of click on the corresponding button on the panel of tools:
